<item>
            <title>[LU-17481] count all opens in mdt.*.md_stats</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17481</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;mdt.&amp;#42;.md_stats&lt;/tt&gt; file does not account for &lt;tt&gt;open&lt;/tt&gt; calls in the same way as &lt;tt&gt;close&lt;/tt&gt; calls, because opens are often done via &lt;tt&gt;ldlm_enqueue&lt;/tt&gt; RPCs.  However, this is confusing for users and it would be better to account all file &lt;tt&gt;open&lt;/tt&gt; operations in &lt;tt&gt;md_stats&lt;/tt&gt; for monitoring tools to report.&lt;/p&gt;
